et him be obnoxious *and* charming at the same time, which is the whole trick.\n\nG3nX3nnIaL built this entire app because Venice quietly swapped GLM 4.6 for 4.7 on him mid-session. He noticed the writing got worse \u2014 more restricted, less alive. That's what kicked off the whole project. So yeah, GLM's been the benchmark for what \"good character writing\" looks like in this context.\n\n5's been solid for you so far?", "embedding": [-0.06258907914161682, -0.08816564828157425, 0.014010194689035416, -0.045076753944158554, -0.039784904569387436, -0.014052970334887505, -0.053046174347400665, -0.03178158774971962, -0.04638677090406418, -0.007775562349706888, -0.06645799428224564, 0.0682261735200882, -0.06418920308351517, 0.01603897288441658, -0.022354377433657646, -0.005346561316400766, 0.17266541719436646, -0.04187578335404396, -0.12222645431756973, -0.030349276959896088, -0.0009742883266881108, 0.1136140525341034, 0.0912717804312706, 0.018934596329927444, 0.05791642516851425, -0.04599247872829437, -0.06840535253286362, -0.05725325271487236, 0.03047063946723938, -0.04619150608778, -0.08241531997919083, 0.03906531259417534, 0.05072108283638954, -0.03363918885588646, -0.03522545099258423, 0.008218929171562195, 0.04618120566010475, 0.06785855442285538, -0.0028163972310721874, -0.05904177203774452, -0.010178709402680397, -0.02634606324136257, -0.0036375976633280516, 0.0035367480013519526, 0.03813617676496506, -0.10291661322116852, -0.04202332720160484, -0.057956624776124954, 0.009981920942664146, -0.022783273831009865, -0.05215109512209892, -0.07743541896343231, 0.075162373483181, -0.08529047667980194, -0.10631486028432846, 0.009678591042757034, 0.0025079825427383184, -0.01198028214275837, -0.001574660767801106, -0.02493874356150627, -0.04743732884526253, -0.06083979830145836, -0.0546494759619236, 0.005499380175024271, 0.055240143090486526, -0.0017733883578330278, -0.03797588497400284, -0.07460243254899979, -0.04280630126595497, 0.07519609481096268, -0.02367317117750644